<p><strong>What is "The Land of Stories: The Enchantress Returns"?</strong></p>
<p>"The Land of Stories: The Enchantress Returns" is the fourth installment in the beloved "The Land of Stories" series by Chris Colfer. The novel continues the adventures of Alex and Conner Bailey, two siblings who discover a magical portal to the fairy tale world of The Land of Stories. In this installment, the evil Enchantress returns, threatening to plunge both worlds into chaos.</p>
